Project rules

Use Next.js with React components.

Use Tailwind CSS for styling.

Keep the design clean, modern and responsive.

Use max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 for main sections.

Use rounded-3xl or rounded-[2rem] for cards.

Use shadow-lg, shadow-xl or shadow-2xl for depth.

Use transition and hover:-translate-y for interactive elements.

Use blue, violet, cyan and slate colors.

Keep text readable on mobile.

Use grid with md:grid-cols-2 or md:grid-cols-4 for responsive layout.

Use clear section ids:
about
skills
experience
projects

Keep buttons visible and clickable on mobile.

Every external link must include target="_blank".

Do not add unused code.

Do not remove existing content unless asked.